# Turkey Tetrazzini

Based on [https://inagarteneats.com/barefoot-contessa-turkey-tetrazzini-recipe](https://inagarteneats.com/barefoot-contessa-turkey-tetrazzini-recipe) or [https://www.southernliving.com/turkey-tetrazzini-8730216](https://www.southernliving.com/turkey-tetrazzini-8730216) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20250427120255/https://www.southernliving.com/turkey-tetrazzini-8730216))

